{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"372667adac","title":"关于第一颗原子弹试爆后现场观察情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c8478deadf","index":0,"year":1964,"month":10,"day":27,"articleId":"372667adac"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"48a28b6c53","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"372667adac","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中国人民解放军副总参谋长、国防科学技术委员会副主任张爱萍和第二机械工业部副部长兼国防科学委员会副主任刘西尧1964年10月26日报告的批语。"},{"id":"3ee675d159","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"372667adac","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张爱萍和刘西尧的报告说：据我们这两天在原子弹试爆现场观察效应试验情况，初步认为，地面暴露的有生物，在一定的距离内，多数将陆续死亡；在一定的距离外，虽不致死亡，但将丧失战斗力。地面暴露配置的各种作战武器，在一定的距离内，大部分被破坏或在短时间不能使用；在一定的距离外，只要稍加防护（如野战拖体），基本上没有影响。各种工事、掩体，特别是地下工事，对原子弹爆炸有很好的防护能力。"}],"contents":[{"id":"28415acc28","type":"title","text":"关于第一颗原子弹试爆后现场观察情况报告的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"372667adac"},{"id":"48a28b6c53","type":"subtitle","text":"只有工事、矮墙、坚房等物，就能防御核爆，不致伤人。P","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"372667adac"},{"id":"3ee675d159","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"372667adac"},{"id":"e0ff5d2af6","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十七日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"372667adac"}],"page":{"id":"25e37fb3de","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"372667adac","start":224,"end":224}}}},"__N_SSG":true}